# Optional: prepend a prospect-branded institution to the picker.
# When set, the picker fetches /api/bank-meta?domain=$NEXT_PUBLIC_PROSPECT_DOMAIN
# and pulls the prospect's real logo, brand color and tagline from their
# homepage at render time. Useful for sales demos.
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PROSPECT_DOMAIN=communitybank.net
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PROSPECT_NAME=Community Bank
